  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a small horror puzzle game that Players will play an amnesiac teenager to escape from the unknown villa, in the process of the story of the mystery will be unraveled one by one ......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(The game has a slightly different ending depending on the level of exploration)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game contains regular puzzle and chase elements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unknown villa ...... Mysterious little girl ...... Fierce female ghost with axe ......Everything in the game is both familiar and unfamiliar, and as the game's story unfolds, mysteries will be revealed ......<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411310/extras/410345f2d48823caa6516e75bdd0aec2.avif?t=1740411521\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411310/extras_big/410345f2d48823caa6516e75bdd0aec2.avif?t=1740411521 width=800 height=612 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Redemption ......<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411310/extras/0f9cf006afbc26b24cc4867c55f1701a.avif?t=1740411521\" width=800 height=650 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Family ......?<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411310/extras/532981dc865464749e404e8441fe1998.avif?t=1740411521\" width=800 height=610 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you're careful and dedicated, after collecting all the memory clues, the title screen will unlock special features that will help you get to the bottom of things.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(In-game scene contains a lot of blood)</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a small horror puzzle game that Players will play an amnesiac teenager to escape from the unknown villa, in the process of the story of the mystery will be unraveled one by one ......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(The game has a slightly different ending depending on the level of exploration)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game contains regular puzzle and chase elements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unknown villa ...... Mysterious little girl ...... Fierce female ghost with axe ......Everything in the game is both familiar and unfamiliar, and as the game's story unfolds, mysteries will be revealed ......<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411310/extras/410345f2d48823caa6516e75bdd0aec2.avif?t=1740411521\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411310/extras_big/410345f2d48823caa6516e75bdd0aec2.avif?t=1740411521 width=800 height=612 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Redemption ......<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411310/extras/0f9cf006afbc26b24cc4867c55f1701a.avif?t=1740411521\" width=800 height=650 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Family ......?<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3411310/extras/532981dc865464749e404e8441fe1998.avif?t=1740411521\" width=800 height=610 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you're careful and dedicated, after collecting all the memory clues, the title screen will unlock special features that will help you get to the bottom of things.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(In-game scene contains a lot of blood)</p>",
